summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of a portion of Blocks 2, 3, 4 and 9, and all of Blocks 8, 10 and 11, Denny's Addition to Ballard and Seattle, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-124 and 17-89, respectively.
